[27/05/2019 07:03:21] <font color="#ffffff"></font>
[27/05/2019 07:03:21] <font color="#ffffff">‘Los Crímenes de Manson.</font>
[27/05/2019 07:03:31] <font color="#ffffff">"Emmanuel Carrer es un novelista</font>
